<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4508593>
    dc:description "Fig. 37. Orthoneolepta fulvipennis (Jacoby, 1884): a, head; b, prothorax; c, meso- and metathorax, ventral view; d, hindwing, right, dorsal view; e, prothoracic; f, mesothoracic; g, metathoracic leg; h, female abdomen; i, male abdomen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4508593/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4508595>
    dc:description "Figs. 38–42. Orthoneolepta fulvipennis (Jacoby, 1884). 38, dorsal colour pattern. 39, antennae: a, male; b, female. 40, median lobe: a, dorsal; b, lateral; c, ventral. 41, three different spermathecae. 42, two pair of bursa sclerites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4508595/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4508601>
    dc:description "Figs. 45–49. Orthoneolepta banggiensis (Mohamedsaid, 1997). 45, dorsal colour pattern. 46, antennae: a, male; b, female. 47, median lobe: a, dorsal; b, lateral; c, ventral. 48, three different spermathecae. 49, two pair of bursa sclerites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4508601/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4508597>
    dc:description "Fig. 43. Distribution of O. fulvipennis (Jacoby, 1884) and O. banggiensis (Mohamedsaid, 1997)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4508597/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4508563>
    dc:description "Figs. 2–6. Neolepta sumatrensis (Jacoby, 1884). 2, dorsal colour pattern. 3, antennae: a, male; b, female. 4, Median lobe: a, dorsal; b, lateral; c, ventral. 5, three different spermathecae. 6, two pairs of bursa sclerites. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4508563/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4508569>
    dc:description "Figs. 10–14. Neolepta quadriplagiata Jacoby, 1886. 10, dorsal colour pattern. 11, antennae: a, male; b, female; 12, median lobe: a, dorsal; b, lateral; c, ventral. 13, three different spermathecae. 14, two pairs of bursa sclerites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4508569/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4508561>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Neolepta sumatrensis (Jacoby, 1884): a, head; b, prothorax; c, meso- and metathorax, ventral view; d, hindwing, right, dorsal view; e, prothoracic leg; f, mesothoracic leg; g, metathoracic leg; h, female abdomen; i, male abdomen. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4508561/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4508575>
    dc:description "Figs. 17–21. Paraneolepta marginata (Jacoby, 1884). 17, dorsal colour pattern. 18, antennae: a, male; b, female. 19, median lobe: a, dorsal; b, lateral; c, ventral. 20, three different spermathecae. 21, two pairs of bursa sclerites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4508575/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4508585>
    dc:description "Figs. 25–29. Paraneolepta limbella (Baly, 1886). 25, dorsal colour pattern. 26, antennae: a, male; b, female. 27, median lobe: a, dorsal; b, lateral; c, ventral. 28, three different spermathecae. 29, one pair of bursa sclerites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4508585/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4508589>
    dc:description "Figs. 31–35. Paraneolepta imitans (Jacoby, 1894). 31, dorsal colour pattern. 32, antennae: a, female; b, male. 33, median lobe: a, dorsal; b, lateral; c, ventral. 34, three different spermathecae. 35, two pairs of bursa sclerites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4508589/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

